757
00:38:51.830 --> 00:38:52.911
Are you sure?

758
00:38:55.959 --> 00:38:58.319
And I think I might be recognizing
a little bit of jealousy.

759
00:38:58.378 --> 00:38:59.994
That's not a good trait. guys.

760
00:39:04.300 --> 00:39:06.667
