802
00:41:04.295 --> 00:41:05.831
Where's my potato chips?

803
00:41:05.922 --> 00:41:08.380
We're not having chips tonight. munchkin.
Sorry.

804
00:41:08.466 --> 00:41:10.253
- I want my chips.
- Lita!

805
00:41:10.343 --> 00:41:12.676
Lizzy. Pete and I worked really hard
