00:41:31.447 --> 00:41:33.905
No. <i>cuatro</i> means "quart."
Like quart of milk.

815
00:41:33.992 --> 00:41:37.076
She said. "You're not gonna have a potato
chip. but you will drink that milk."

816
00:41:37.161 --> 00:41:39.574
