832
00:42:16.409 --> 00:42:18.901
These are really. really good potatoes.

833
00:42:22.749 --> 00:42:24.581
- God!
- Oh. my God. Are you okay?

834
00:42:24.667 --> 00:42:25.748
Oh. God.

835
00:42:27.003 --> 00:42:28.414
Lita. duck!

