869
00:44:02.598 --> 00:44:05.090
Yeah. Lizzy. you body-positive whore!

870
00:44:05.184 --> 00:44:07.972
Okay. you're done.
Gimme that. Give it to me.

871
00:44:08.062 --> 00:44:09.662
